@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.abs(v0) * wp.abs(wp.abs(v1 + 0.11)))
    v2 = wp.cos(0.44)
    tmp = 0.78
    v2 = ((v0 - (v1 + 0.15 - v1 + 0.23)) - ((tmp + 0.39 / tmp + 0.64) * wp.sin(tmp + 0.96)))
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.54)) + (v2 * 0.50))
    v1 = 0.47
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.exp(v1 + 0.80) + (v1 + 0.49 + tmp + 0.41)))
    data[tid] = v0
